    },
    {
      "Description": "Implement custom Triton kernels for sparse attention, focusing on block sparsity and partial fusion.",
      "Metrics": "Kernel performance, including latency, memory usage, and throughput.",
      "Method": "Profile the kernels using nvprof and Nsight, focusing on warp stall reasons, achieved bandwidth, and occupancy. Optimize the kernels iteratively based on the profiling results."
