      "Description": "Evaluate the performance of the sparse attention kernels on the same transformer models and configurations as the dense baseline.",
      "Metrics": "Latency, memory usage, throughput, and accuracy.",
      "Method": "Compare the results of the sparse attention implementation with the dense baseline, ensuring the same model accuracy is maintained or improved."
    },
    {
      "Description": "Conduct A/B latency races under fixed accuracy budgets to quantify the performance gains.",
      "Metrics": "p50/p99 latency, throughput under batching, and energy per token.",
      "Method": "Run multiple inference trials on the same hardware with different configurations, measuring the latency and throughput for each trial. Report the results with variance across runs."
    }
  ],
